**Version Used**: Local build of latest main revision, da6cf36ff1a922f17e93a07eab561275707414a1, i.e. already containing the fix #82041.

**Steps to Reproduce**:
Invoke "Use coalesce expression" on the if statement.
```csharp
class D
{
    public void M()
    {
        var value = M2();
        // Test
        if (value == null)
        {
            throw new InvalidOperationException();
        }
    }

    string? M2() => null;
}
```

**Expected Behavior**: The comment is placed before or after the rewritten statement.

**Actual Behavior**: The comment is dropped.

